docs {
  ## List Request For Pricing
  แสดงรายการใบขอราคาทั้งหมดพร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและค้นหา

  Lists all Request for Pricing (RFP) documents within the business unit, allowing procurement staff to track and compare competitive pricing submissions from multiple vendors.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `page` | number | No | 1 | Page number |
  | `perpage` | number | No | 10 | Items per page |
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "name": "Q1 2026 Pricing Request",
        "pricelist_template_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4e",
        "start_date": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z",
        "end_date": "2026-04-30T23:59:59.000Z",
        "workflow_current_stage": "draft",
        "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 5,
      "total": 42,
      "prev": null,
      "next": 2
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid Bearer token |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}
